tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: A nice, small, compact, well equipped, and well staffed  dental clinic, with a versatile doctor Archak. Dr. Archak is a confident and enthusiastic dentist, who knows her job well and dexterous at what she does. She took all the pains to explain to me patiently the various options for my problem, and helped me make an informed choice. Her suggestions are thorough and comprehensive, keeping in mind the long term viability of the solution. Her interactions are highly professional, courteous, and results driven, with a personal touch. She is a detail oriented perfectionist who does not seem to settle with doing anything sub-optimal. Any work done by her comes out clean and neat. I got done multiple fillings and two caps (total of 5 capped teeth ). All this happened over like 5-6 sittings. The fit and feel of the cap is just perfect . I have had experience with several dentists in the past - fitting a cap properly has required multiple visits to trim, align the bite, etc.  But Dr, Archak just needed one session to fit the two caps perfectly. She felt like a highly experienced dentist though my understanding is she is probably much younger. Her charges are affordable.  Perhaps there are places that are a little cheaper, but she is a hard to find dentist for the dexterity and expertise she possesses, and the quality she delivers. Highly recommend her.
reply_text: Thank you so much sir first of all for your patience to type whole thing. I'm happy to see it.Hope doing all good keep smiling.

review: * **** *** ******* ***** **** ***** ** ***** ** ***** ** ****** ******** I visited the clinic initially and was charged 16000 for cyst removal in wisdom tooth and she advised for surgery but everytime cost was asked, she would say "Depends on surgery" and didn't even give an estimate. As a doctor I was suspicious and enquired around a few clinics and an OMF surgeon along with getting an estimate in a hospital and learnt that this was overcharging and it hurt that I was laughed at for what happened inspite of being a doctor.
